Package: nisrarr
Title: Download Data from the NISRA Data Portal
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Mark", "Paulin", email =
        "paulin.mark@googlemail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Download data from the Northern Ireland Statistics and
        Research Agency (NISRA) data portal, accessed at
        <https://data.nisra.gov.uk>. NISRA is a government agency and
        the principal source of official statistics and social research
        on Northern Ireland.
